  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to libnsl</title>

    <para>
      The <application>libnsl</application> package contains the public client
      interface for NIS(YP) and NIS+. It replaces the NIS library that used to
      be in glibc.
    </para>

    &lfs90_checked;

